  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><div style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/32px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/48px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/64px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/32px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/48px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/64px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/32px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/48px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/64px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell_of_Brightwater_Keep\" title=\"House Tyrell of Brightwater Keep\"><img alt=\"Garlan Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Garlan_Tyrell.svg/32px-Garlan_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Garlan_Tyrell.svg/48px-Garlan_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Garlan_Tyrell.svg/64px-Garlan_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;text-align:center\">Leonette Fossoway</span></div></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Garlan Tyrell and Leonette Fossoway by Jroahn.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/14/Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg/350px-Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/14/Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg/525px-Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/14/Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg/700px-Garlan_Tyrell_and_Leonette_Fossoway_by_Jroahn.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Garlan and Leonette, by Jroahn</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Brightwater_Keep\" title=\"Brightwater Keep\">Brightwater Keep</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway\" title=\"House Fossoway\">House Fossoway</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell of Highgarden</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell_of_Brightwater_Keep\" title=\"House Tyrell of Brightwater Keep\">House Tyrell of Brightwater Keep</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Leonette Fossoway</b> is the wife of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan Tyrell</a>. She is a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway\" title=\"House Fossoway\">House Fossoway</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> though it is unclear which branch of the family she is from.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Leonette\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Leonette</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leonette_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Leonette is dainty and bright-eyed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> She plays the high <a href=\"/index.php/Harp\" title=\"Harp\">harp</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leonette_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leonette_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady Leonette is among <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>'s retinue when she comes to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. Margaery introduces Leonette to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> over dinner in the <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenvault\" title=\"Maidenvault\">Maidenvault</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> For his valor during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>, Garlan is granted the lordship of <a href=\"/index.php/Brightwater_Keep\" title=\"Brightwater Keep\">Brightwater Keep</a>, making Leonette the Lady of Brightwater Keep.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> She later teaches the high harp to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Leonette and Garlan attend Sansa's wedding to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>. Noticing Sansa's deep sadness over the marriage, Leonette expresses her concerns to her husband, who tries to assuage Sansa's fears about marrying Tyrion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Her and Garlan later attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">royal wedding</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a> and Margaery, seated at the high table next to Sansa and Tyrion. Leonette jests with Garlan and Tyrion at the expense of the singers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Leonette\">Quotes by Leonette</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leonette_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Leonette\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Perhaps you should be a singer, my <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>. You rhyme as well as this <a href=\"/index.php/Galyeon_of_Cuy\" title=\"Galyeon of Cuy\">Galyeon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Leonette to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leonette_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"refere